Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这就是卡拉OK包厢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙小姐头一次来卡拉OK吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真是非常的新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妹妹没来过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没有过  我们兴趣不合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是该问「你为什么在这里」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为仁君也在这里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…能不能不要贴我太近…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要太粘他了  没看到仁他不愿意么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得你异常地受欢迎啊  御厨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么从他脸上看不出喜悦的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  已经有人点歌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  反正是随便点嘛  就当BGM了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开场肯定要这个才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:56.08,LS_EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（宇宙鉄人  キョーダイン）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:56.08,LS_EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（宇宙铁人　兄弟）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从各方面来讲…这有点…那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么火星歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道是早在我们出生之前的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊  要杵在那里到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快过来坐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书上面的歌都可以挑出来唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个歌手的名字该怎么念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我不太了解这方面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是暗潮汹涌呢  从各种意义来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  今天是为了培养大家感情才来唱卡拉OK的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  给我搞热闹一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这时候还培养什么感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话  浪费时间  谁先来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  优柔寡断！猜拳啦猜拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁输谁打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好  不会唱歌的女孩子拼命唱歌的样子真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵子  你真变态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的啦  让我打头阵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁君喜欢什么样的歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  倒也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是大铁君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没听过大铁君唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来我也没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是天赐良机么  让我们听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就唱首慢歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一般人来说还真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人着迷的低音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个被艺术之神宠爱的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他起错名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱得好棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这个按钮是这用处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大铁  唱得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…只是很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是头一次唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常我都没唱过歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁君？你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来到谁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:37.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（连妈妈也★可爱！）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你要唱这个就帮你选了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不唱这么甜的动画歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选什么流行歌啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多少也是懂气氛的人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！快去唱动画歌！唱动画歌！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要唱你自己极力推荐的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是哪门子的羞耻Play啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱得还好  曲子也那样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御厨  你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我再叫一杯柠檬苏打水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个  我们要续一杯柠檬苏打水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年前的OVA「妖兽机神混沌刃」的插曲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「和你一起逃亡」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我推荐的歌曲啊！混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很燃的吧？很激情对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看宅男！白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵子你真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也是头一次来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我对唱吧  就这样吧就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要那样还不如我一个人唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好微妙  特别是那个生硬的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话的确很有御厨风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们的柠檬苏打水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空杯子让我收一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柠檬苏打水  再加一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一首！再来一首！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…御厨泪奔了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…那是因为害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半已经呵呵带喘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他能唱到最后已经很赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个  该薙小姐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  感觉好兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把这份信心分给仁一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过  已经足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙小姐给了仁很多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为以前的仁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在人前唱歌简直是不敢想像的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从和薙小姐一起过日子之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微变了一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是第一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱不好是情有可原的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是第一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…也倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大铁真棒啊  什么都做得来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人只会半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是着急的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地熟练了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大铁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌也是  画也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有你的长处  一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大铁  接下来你唱什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？还有接下来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…啥玩意儿  那歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆制食品  「Hello大豆之歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　　CM SONG{\r}\N啊  那首广告歌曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎么会知道这首歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是TATSUYA留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超市尻毛屋」我也能唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薙基本上只能借这种歌来用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花样年华但没少女情怀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿的？哪儿的TATSUYA？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花样年华但没少女情怀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  打搅你们的热情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该轮到学姐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你对大家那个指手划脚的架势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必一定很能唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  就让我们来倾听一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是的  秋叶君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵子一旦唱起来的话可拦不住的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好强大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很强很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忏悔妹妹你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去补妆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你问我怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你甩给我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与平时若似若离的动漫音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连动作都那么完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刚才那一曲的质量  就算直接发单曲也不为过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能唱这首歌的不仅限于10岁左右么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘我就是十几岁啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是反动力啦  反动力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反动力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有反动力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们接受个屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就这兴趣怎么着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我想利用最后一轮显眼一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种冲击力太犯规了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没有什么拿手的好歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？在卡拉OK唱童谣不就是个内向到家的笨蛋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  知道了  我说重了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也想让他喜欢上你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你还想接着唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你看谁都不唱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个应该是忏悔妹妹了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…貌似还没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会自觉地逃跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真够晚的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干啥去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去开了个作战小会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来该到我出场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  按顺序嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌曲总会暴露出唱歌人的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们互相熟知的绝佳机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「豆制大豆」不算在内！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「Hello大豆」！豆制食品的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经传出CD出道传言的本姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们听一下真正的女生歌曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会有这种发展…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁君～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我无法坐在你旁边也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…我希望你的心里总有我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈——？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很差很可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义  与贵子正相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真够感动的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下！你这样子不是犯规吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌就是这种需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁不是很烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱卡拉OK的技术难度有这么高吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了？那么…第二遍  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是对唱时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大铁  我们一起唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  出了一身怪汗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  异常的疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊…总觉得忘记了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  紫乃前辈还没唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  太狡猾了前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫乃？ 不能让她唱的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她会开眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  一定要我唱的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的神薙…哎  薙？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:39.98,biaoti2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,165)\fn@方正行楷_GBK}{\frz-90}一切尽在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:39.98,biaoti2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,225)\fn@方正行楷_GBK}{\frz-90}灯火阑珊处
